sfdmu:run.description:
The Salesforce DX data migration tool.
Populate your org (scratch/development/sandbox/production) with data imported from another org or CSV file.
Refer https://github.com/forcedotcom/SFDX-Data-Move-Utility for the detailed help information.

json.name: json
json.description: [Optional] Format the command output as json

loglevel.name: loglevel
loglevel.description: logging level for this command invocation

targetusername.name: targetusername
targetusername.description: username or alias for the target org; overrides default target org

apiversion.name: apiversion
apiversion.description: [Optional] Override the api version set in the package definition

sourceusername.name: sourceusername
sourceusername.description: Source org username/alias or 'csvfile' for csv load

verbose.name: verbose
verbose.description: [Optional] Emit additional command output to stdout

concise.name: concise
concise.description: [Optional] Emit brief command output to stdout

version.name: version
version.description: [Optional] Output the current version of the plugin

filelog.name: filelog
filelog.description: [Optional] Enable additional logging into log file
